---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Parent Support | Rabbia Psychologist — NeuroCare Child Development Services"
  description="Parent guidance for developmental concerns, behaviour challenges, ASD/ADHD questions, emotional regulation, school concerns, report confusion, and home support planning."
>
  <div class="bg-brand-cream py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Parent Guidance for Child Development Concerns</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        When parents feel confused about behaviour, school feedback, developmental delays, ASD/ADHD questions, or reports, Rabbia Psychologist — NeuroCare Child Development Services helps them understand the concern and take practical next steps.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl space-y-12">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">When parent support can help</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We help parents when they face uncertainty about their child's development, need strategies for daily routines, or require clarity following a professional assessment.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Common concerns parents bring</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>Behavioral and emotional regulation challenges</li>
          <li>School-related concerns or IEP navigation</li>
          <li>ASD or ADHD management</li>
          <li>Questions about developmental milestones</li>
          <li>Confusion regarding assessment reports</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">What happens in a parent guidance session</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We discuss your child's current challenges, review any relevant reports or feedback, and work collaboratively to form a structured, actionable plan.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">What you may receive after the session</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Depending on the consultation, you may receive tailored resources, a structured support plan, behavioral strategies, or clear next-step recommendations.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Between-session support options</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We offer specialized plans to help you maintain consistency and momentum between your child's therapy or school sessions.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Overseas Pakistani and international family support</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We proudly support families globally, bridging the gap between local resources and continuous, culturally-aware developmental guidance.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/book" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-brand-navy text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-900 transition-all shadow-lg">
          Book Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
